history.content: Probably reasonable (though likely challenging) assuming your other classes aren't too heavy. With 162 and 184, you'll pretty much always have 1 or 2 projects ongoing at any point in time that you'll be working on. Fortunately, 184's projects are individual, so you won't have to coordinate two different project groups at the same time.
